cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper proposes a technique for learning features using 1D convolutions, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) communities. The paper also discusses the computational efficiency of the proposed method, which is relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) communities. Finally, the paper presents large-scale experiments on image classification, which is relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) community.
